            NADP+ [CPD:C00006]
PRODUCT     4-(dimethylamino)azobenzene;
            NADPH [CPD:C00005];
            H+ [CPD:C00080]
COMMENT     The reaction occurs in the reverse direction to that shown above. Other azo dyes, such as Methyl Red, Rocceline, Solar Orange and Sumifix Black B can also be reduced [2].
